{"id":308265,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/08/global-voices-新加坡的媒体与审查/","date":"2013-08-10T04:15:29Z","modified":"2013-08-10T04:15:29Z","title":"Global Voices | 新加坡的媒体与审查","content":"<p><p>在新加坡一家重要报社担任副编辑三年后，Mark Fenn<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.asiasentinel.com/index.php?option=com_content&#038;task=view&#038;id=5571&#038;Itemid=181\">说明</a>新加坡如何执行审查：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>报纸的控制，除了公然行使，也透过更为精妙的手段。同时，自我审查无所不在。</p>\n<p>对记者来说，在很后面的阶段，因为“新闻人物”或是某政府机关想更改发言或头条的用字，而得修改报导内容的情形并不罕见。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><span><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/mong/\" title=\"文章导读 Mong Palatino\">Mong Palatino</a></span> · <span>译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/ameli/\" title=\"文章导读 Ameli\">Ameli</a></span></span>  · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2013/08/03/singapore-media-and-censorship/\" title=\"阅读原文  en\">阅读原文  en</a></span> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2013/08/10/12759/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br /><span><span>分享: </span> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%AA%92%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%A1%E6%9F%A5&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F08%2F10%2F12759%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F08%2F10%2F12759%2F&#038;desc=%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%AA%92%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%A1%E6%9F%A5\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/\" onclick=\"javascript:var js=document.createElement (\" t